queries.sparql:
PREFIX fno: <http://w3id.org/function/ontology#>
PREFIX grel: <http://semweb.datasciencelab.be/ns/grel#>
PREFIX : <https://fno.io/prov/dbpedia/iswc2017-semsci#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

SELECT ?f ?iValue ?oValue WHERE {
  ?e a fno:Execution ;
    fno:executes ?f .
  ?e grel:stringInput ?i .
  ?e grel:stringOutput ?o .
  ?i rdf:value ?iValue .
  ?o rdf:value ?oValue .
}
queries.name: All input output values
